<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MECENATE STUDIO - Cinematic Identities</title>
    <style>
        /* TIPOGRAFÍA Y VARIABLES ESTILO A24 */
        :root {
            --font-main: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            --color-bg: #ffffff; 
            --color-text: #000000;
            --color-grey-bg: #f4f4f4;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            background-color: var(--color-bg);
            color: var(--color-text);
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* HEADER COMPLETAMENTE CENTRADO */
        header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 30px 40px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 12px; 
            padding-left: 52px; 
            z-index: 100;
            background-color: #ffffff; 
            color: #000000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            transition: transform 0.4s ease-in-out;
        }

        .header-hidden {
            transform: translateY(-100%);
        }

        /* HERO VIDEO */
        .hero-section {
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #000;
            position: relative;
            padding-top: 70px; 
        }

        .hero-section video {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        /* SECCIÓN DE SERVICIOS - DISEÑO ZIG-ZAG */
        .services-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .service-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            text-decoration: none; 
            color: var(--color-text);
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .service-row:hover .service-image-container img {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        /* Clases para alternar el orden (Imagen a la izquierda) */
        @media (min-width: 901px) {
            .service-row.image-left .service-text { order: 2; }
            .service-row.image-left .service-image-container { order: 1; }
        }

        /* Columna de Texto */
        .service-text {
            padding: 10vw 6vw;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .service-category {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #777;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .service-title {
            font-size: clamp(45px, 6vw, 85px);
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 0.92;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 95%;
        }

        .service-action {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .arrow { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 300; }

        /* Columna de Imagen */
        .service-image-container {
            background-color: var(--color-grey-bg);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 6vw; 
        }

        .service-image-container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            aspect-ratio: 4 / 3; 
            object-fit: cover;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); 
            transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
        }
.service-image-container img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            aspect-ratio: 4 / 3; 
            object-fit: cover;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); 
            transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
            /* EL TOQUE A24: Blanco y negro, más contraste y ligeramente más oscura */
            filter: grayscale(100%) contrast(125%) brightness(90%);
        }

        /* FRAME DE RESPIRO */
        .breathing-frame {
            padding: 150px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

    .breathing-text {font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px); 
    font-weight: 500; /* Bajamos de 700 a 500 para quitarle peso visual */
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 4px; /* Más espacio entre letras da un aire muy editorial */
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.2;    }
.about-subtitle {
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 400; 
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 60px; /* Más margen inferior para separar visualmente tu nombre de la lista */
    color: #888;
}
        /* RECORRIDO ACADÉMICO (TU INFORMACIÓN ORIGINAL) */
        .about-section {
            padding: 100px 40px;
            max-width: 1800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 60px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-image {
            aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(100%); 
            transition: transform 0.8s ease;
        }

        .about-image:hover img { transform: scale(1.02); }

        .about-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .about-title {
            font-size: clamp(40px, 4vw, 60px);
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .about-subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .academic-timeline {
            list-style: none;
            border-top: 2px solid #000;
        }

        .academic-timeline li {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 25px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .academic-timeline span.degree {
            flex-grow: 1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding-right: 20px;
        }

        .academic-timeline span.school {
            text-align: right;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* INFORMACIÓN PERSONAL Y CONTACTO (TU FOOTER ORIGINAL) */
        .footer-info {
            padding: 100px 40px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 50px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .info-block p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .credits-list { list-style: none; }

        .credits-list li {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            padding: 15px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .credits-list span:first-child { font-weight: 700; }

        /* OPTIMIZACIÓN MOBILE */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            header { padding: 20px 20px 20px 32px; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 8px; }
            
            .service-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column; 
            }
            
            /* En móvil forzamos siempre el texto arriba y la imagen abajo */
            .service-text {
                padding: 60px 30px 40px 30px;
                order: 1 !important; 
            }
            
            .service-image-container {
                padding: 40px 30px 60px 30px;
                order: 2 !important; 
                background-color: #ffffff; 
            }

            .service-image-container img { box-shadow: none; }

            .breathing-frame { padding: 100px 20px; }
            .about-section { padding: 0 20px 60px 20px; }
            .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
            .academic-timeline li { 
                flex-direction: column; 
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            .academic-timeline span.school { text-align: left; }
            .footer-info { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 60px 20px; gap: 40px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header id="main-header">
        <div>MECENATE</div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero-section">
        <video autoplay loop muted playsinline>
            <source src="hero.mov" type="video/quicktime">
        </video>
    </section>

    <section class="services-wrapper">
        
        <a href="relatos.html" class="service-row image-left">
            <div class="service-text">
                <span class="service-category">Film & Direction</span>
                <h2 class="service-title">Relatos visuales cinematográficos.</h2>
                <div class="service-action"><span class="arrow">⟶</span> Ver Proyectos</div>
            </div>
            <div class="service-image-container">
                <img src="foto1.jpg" alt="Relatos visuales cinematográficos">
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="digital-spaces.html" class="service-row">
            <div class="service-text">
                <span class="service-category">Digital Spaces</span>
                <h2 class="service-title">Sitios web de autor.</h2>
                <div class="service-action"><span class="arrow">⟶</span> Ver Proyectos</div>
            </div>
            <div class="service-image-container">
                <img src="foto2.jpg" alt="Sitios web de autor">
            </div>
        </a>

       <a href="strategy.html" class="service-row image-left">
            <div class="service-text">
                <span class="service-category">Strategy & Curation</span>
                <h2 class="service-title">Gestión de redes y ecosistema.</h2>
                <div class="service-action"><span class="arrow">⟶</span> Ver Proyectos</div>
            </div>
            <div class="service-image-container">
                <img src="foto3.jpg" alt="Estrategia digital y redes">
            </div>
        </a>

    </section>

    <section class="breathing-frame">
        <p class="breathing-text">"El silencio visual y la composición cuidada son el verdadero lujo para que tu marca destaque en la era digital."</p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="gilbert-foto.jpg" alt="Retrato de Gilbert Charris">
            </div>
            <div class="about-text">
                <h2 class="about-title">Gilbert Charris</h2>
                <h3 class="about-subtitle">Director & Lead Designer</h3>
                
                <ul class="academic-timeline">
                    <li>
                        <span class="degree">Master International Filmmaking</span>
                        <span class="school">Scola Superior de Cine de Catalunya, Barcelona - Roma</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="degree">Grado en Diseño para la Industria Sostenible y el Territorio</span>
                        <span class="school">Roma</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="degree">Master in Marketing Cultural</span>
                        <span class="school">Gemma Business School Roma</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer-info">
        <div class="info-block">
            <h3 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; text-transform: uppercase;">La Agencia</h3>
            <p>Mecenate Studio transforma espacios y marcas en relatos cinematográficos inolvidables. Dominamos el entorno digital y el espacio urbano para crear un ecosistema visual coherente, posicionando a tu proyecto como un referente de autor.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-block">
            <ul class="credits-list">
                <li><span>Director</span> <span>Gilbert Charris</span></li>
                <li><span>Base</span> <span>Barcelona / Rome</span></li>
                <li><span>Expertise</span> <span>Cinematography & Web Design</span></li>
                <li><span>Email</span> <span>Gilberto-charris@hotmail.com</span></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        let lastScrollTop = 0;
        let scrollTimeout;
        const header = document.getElementById('main-header');

        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            let scrollTop = window.pageYOffset || document.documentElement.scrollTop;
            
            window.clearTimeout(scrollTimeout);

            if (scrollTop > lastScrollTop) {
                header.classList.add('header-hidden');
            } else {
                header.classList.remove('header-hidden');
            }
            
            lastScrollTop = scrollTop <= 0 ? 0 : scrollTop;

            scrollTimeout = setTimeout(() => {
                if (scrollTop > 50) {
                    header.classList.add('header-hidden');
                }
            }, 1500); 
        });
    </script>

</body>
</html>
